10
00:01:16,571 --> 00:01:18,661
Nobody can save me

11
00:01:19,211 --> 00:01:21,841
God, I have only one request

12
00:01:21,841 --> 00:01:25,471
Stop tearing apart my love

13
00:01:25,881 --> 00:01:28,811
