which would you prefer?

154
00:08:02,341 --> 00:08:04,471
Just call me Kyosuke, Sa-chan.

155
00:08:10,881 --> 00:08:12,471
That's gonna be trouble.

156
00:08:12,991 --> 00:08:13,511
Huh?

157
00:08:13,951 --> 00:08:19,481
Well, I'm more for the dark-skinned
big girls like you, but...

158
00:08:19,691 --> 00:08:20,391
Huh?!

159
00:08:20,531 --> 00:08:22,121
Well, excuse me for
my dark skin.

160
00:08:22,691 --> 00:08:24,991
But even I find her cute.

161
00:08:25,501 --> 00:08:27,121
This is definitely bad.

162
00:09:16,351 --> 00:09:17,821
So cool!

163
00:09:20,021 --> 00:09:22,251
Shin, I didn't notice you there.

164
00:09:22,391 --> 00:09:23,461
Awesome.

165
00:09:23,461 --> 00:09:25,121
I never knew you could play
the drums too, Nana.

166
00:09:25,291 --> 00:09:26,351
I can't.

167
00:09:26,491 --> 00:09:27,651
But you were!

168
00:09:28,191 --> 00:09:29,591
This is all I know.

169
00:09:29,961 --> 00:09:32,491
But you're good.
When did you learn?

170
00:09:33,401 --> 00:09:36,771
Back home while I was in a band,
I learned it for fun.

171
00:09:37,501 --> 00:09:38,561
From Yasu?

172
00:09:39,641 --> 00:09:41,271
