take him seriously

192
00:10:42,771 --> 00:10:44,531
if he said he was
a junior high student.

193
00:10:44,841 --> 00:10:47,241
Oh, but it's April,
so maybe he's in tenth grade now.

194
00:10:47,571 --> 00:10:49,131
